text:
No, it's really great. It fits me perfectly,
almost too perfectly...

Oh! It looks really good on you.
Even better than I imagined.

It's not... I mean, it's not about that.
It's just that the size fits perfectly.

I was wondering if it was necessary
to measure so precisely.

Even when moving around a lot, it doesn't get in
the way at all... It really feels like it's made just for me.

Yeah, that's right. I want you to jump onto the stage
full of energy in this outfit, Juri.

Well...
Thanks, I'll do my best...!
